description: Deletes the specified change set. Deleting change sets ensures that no one executes the wrong change set. If the call successfully completes, CloudFormation successfully deleted the change set. If IncludeNestedStacks specifies True during the creation of the nested change set, then DeleteChangeSet will delete all change sets that belong to the stacks hierarchy and will also delete all change sets for nested stacks with the status of REVIEW_IN_PROGRESS.

parameters.name: ChangeSetName
parameters.description: The name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the change set that you want to delete.
